1
00:00:07,400 --> 00:00:11,460
♪Just To Meet You, you fell for me♪

2
00:00:11,480 --> 00:00:15,460
♪Just to meet me, into my trap you fell♪

3
00:00:15,460 --> 00:00:19,240
♪Wanna try a breathless love?♪

4
00:00:19,240 --> 00:00:23,490
♪Every move hits the heart, close and sure♪

5
00:00:23,490 --> 00:00:27,460
♪Just To Meet You, you love my playful charm♪

6
00:00:27,460 --> 00:00:31,480
♪Just to meet me,
my romantic little schemes for you♪

7
00:00:31,480 --> 00:00:35,170
♪Wanna play another brand-new game?♪

8
00:00:35,170 --> 00:00:40,360
♪Layer by layer, we close the gap♪

9
00:00:40,380 --> 00:00:47,140
=Just To Meet You=

10
00:00:47,140 --> 00:00:48,740
=Episode 7=
=Jiang Niannian Sets the Bait=

11
00:00:49,670 --> 00:00:51,350
Master, please have some porridge.

12
00:00:57,600 --> 00:00:58,440
Master,

13
00:00:59,000 --> 00:01:01,240
Ms. Qingqing's manners and upbringing

14
00:01:01,520 --> 00:01:02,710
are truly top-notch.

15
00:01:03,200 --> 00:01:04,120
She's thoughtful too.

16
00:01:04,840 --> 00:01:06,840
Look, the porridge's gone cold.

17
00:01:07,430 --> 00:01:09,120
She hasn't moved her knees once.

18
00:01:11,430 --> 00:01:12,270
Where's Ye Lang?

19
00:01:12,560 --> 00:01:13,410
Father.

20
00:01:13,430 --> 00:01:15,230
I didn't see my brother at work today.

21
00:01:15,790 --> 00:01:17,040
He must be busy.

22
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:19,480
What's he so busy with?

23
00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:20,840
Master.

24
00:01:21,040 --> 00:01:21,880
If you ask me,

25
00:01:22,560 --> 00:01:23,840
Young Master should

26
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:26,000
get engaged to Ms. Qingqing ASAP.

27
00:01:26,790 --> 00:01:28,280
Ms. Qingqing is a Jiang too.

28
00:01:28,710 --> 00:01:29,950
So outsiders won't gossip.

29
00:01:30,790 --> 00:01:31,630
Besides,

30
00:01:31,640 --> 00:01:32,640
she's so sensible.

31
00:01:33,120 --> 00:01:35,000
She could definitely help him settle down.

32
00:01:35,150 --> 00:01:35,990
Liu.

33
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:37,510
Make me some hangover soup.

34
00:01:38,040 --> 00:01:39,430
So you finally came back.

35
00:01:49,400 --> 00:01:50,240
She...

36
00:01:50,870 --> 00:01:51,710
You...

37
00:01:51,870 --> 00:01:53,510
What are you trying to do?

38
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:56,120
Young Master.

39
00:01:56,420 --> 00:01:57,270
Look,

40
00:01:57,280 --> 00:01:58,560
I was just talking to Master

41
00:01:58,680 --> 00:02:00,590
about your marriage to Ms. Qingqing.

42
00:02:02,430 --> 00:02:03,350
Ye Lang,

43
00:02:05,120 --> 00:02:06,480
I feel dizzy.

44
00:02:07,230 --> 00:02:08,680
That drink you gave me

45
00:02:09,080 --> 00:02:09,920
was too strong.

46
00:02:11,310 --> 00:02:12,590
I want to go rest.

47
00:02:16,590 --> 00:02:17,430
I've said it before

48
00:02:18,680 --> 00:02:21,080
Jiang Niannian is my only wife.

49
00:02:21,960 --> 00:02:23,280
From now on, my daily needs

50
00:02:24,190 --> 00:02:25,960
will be handled directly by her.

51
00:02:27,020 --> 00:02:28,080
Ye Lang, what did you say?

52
00:02:28,430 --> 00:02:29,470
Your wife?

53
00:02:29,870 --> 00:02:30,710
Qingqing,

54
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:31,870
don't worry.

55
00:02:33,310 --> 00:02:34,590
As for Jiang Qingqing,

56
00:02:35,430 --> 00:02:36,590
I think you've got it wrong.

57
00:02:37,520 --> 00:02:39,030
She's only my guest.

58
00:02:40,020 --> 00:02:40,870
I'm not a guest.

59
00:02:40,870 --> 00:02:41,710
Ye Lang.

60
00:02:41,800 --> 00:02:43,520
You said I was your companion.

61
00:02:44,240 --> 00:02:45,280
- I...
- Did I?

62
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:48,120
Then explain
what happened that day right here.

63
00:02:49,280 --> 00:02:50,710
Know your place.

64
00:02:51,240 --> 00:02:52,120
Finish this meal,

65
00:02:53,840 --> 00:02:54,680
and you can leave.

66
00:02:59,710 --> 00:03:00,870
Looks like Young Master

67
00:03:01,630 --> 00:03:02,680
really cares for

68
00:03:03,280 --> 00:03:04,840
Jiang Niannian.

69
00:03:08,150 --> 00:03:08,990
Qingqing,

70
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:10,360
Master and I

71
00:03:10,590 --> 00:03:12,430
truly hoped you'd marry in.

72
00:03:13,150 --> 00:03:16,870
But Ye Lang's heart
is completely taken by your sister.

73
00:03:18,680 --> 00:03:19,590
(Jiang Niannian.)

74
00:03:20,080 --> 00:03:23,190
(I'll make you repay this humiliation.)

75
00:03:28,800 --> 00:03:30,360
(That photo of Xiaodi)

76
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:32,310
(must have been sent by someone here.)

77
00:03:33,240 --> 00:03:34,840
(Xiaodi is in their hands.)

78
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:37,840
(Sorry, Ye Lang.)

79
00:03:43,630 --> 00:03:45,310
Mr. Zhong, you've worked hard for years.

80
00:03:46,240 --> 00:03:47,080
From now on,

81
00:03:47,750 --> 00:03:49,000
I'll prepare Ye Lang's medicine.

82
00:03:50,080 --> 00:03:51,120
Preparing medicine

83
00:03:51,590 --> 00:03:53,120
is no child's play.

84
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:55,080
Ms. Jiang.

85
00:03:55,680 --> 00:03:57,560
Be careful you don't turn it into poison

86
00:03:58,000 --> 00:03:59,190
and cause a disaster.

87
00:04:14,840 --> 00:04:15,680
Ye Lang.

88
00:04:16,480 --> 00:04:17,430
Right now,

89
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:19,830
you can only dance to my tune.

90
00:04:33,190 --> 00:04:34,030
Try it.

91
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:36,840
You made all of this?

92
00:04:37,070 --> 00:04:37,910
Yep.

93
00:04:46,360 --> 00:04:47,510
See if you like it.

94
00:04:57,590 --> 00:04:58,440
Don't wipe it away.

95
00:05:30,190 --> 00:05:31,040
Have more sweets,

96
00:05:31,950 --> 00:05:33,270
then life won't be so bitter.

97
00:05:37,310 --> 00:05:38,750
My mom used to say that

98
00:05:39,310 --> 00:05:40,190
when she was alive.

99
00:05:41,600 --> 00:05:42,510
(Of course I know.)

100
00:05:43,870 --> 00:05:45,390
(Because you told me that)

101
00:05:45,390 --> 00:05:46,310
(in our previous life.)

102
00:05:48,240 --> 00:05:49,080
Come on, try it.

103
00:05:49,560 --> 00:05:50,400
Mm.

104
00:06:04,430 --> 00:06:05,270
Also this one.

105
00:06:14,390 --> 00:06:15,230
Ye Lang.

106
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:16,840
Ye Lang!

107
00:06:17,070 --> 00:06:17,910
Ye Lang!

108
00:06:22,430 --> 00:06:23,270
Someone, hurry!

109
00:06:23,380 --> 00:06:25,020
Young Master coughed up blood and fainted!

110
00:06:25,300 --> 00:06:28,100
(In Surgery)

111
00:06:32,140 --> 00:06:33,190
His condition is critical.

112
00:06:33,750 --> 00:06:34,590
It's poisoning.

113
00:06:35,240 --> 00:06:36,920
I'm issuing a critical notice now.

114
00:06:37,310 --> 00:06:38,870
Move him to the ICU for observation.

115
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:42,640
Poisoning?

116
00:06:43,830 --> 00:06:44,670
Investigate it.

117
00:06:44,920 --> 00:06:45,950
Do find out

118
00:06:46,310 --> 00:06:48,070
who did this.

119
00:06:48,960 --> 00:06:49,800
Master.

120
00:06:49,810 --> 00:06:51,480
These past few days,

121
00:06:52,070 --> 00:06:53,390
Ms. Jiang handled his meals.

122
00:06:55,240 --> 00:06:56,080
Mr. Zhong.

123
00:06:57,390 --> 00:06:58,230
What do you mean?

124
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:00,440
Jiang Niannian.

125
00:07:01,950 --> 00:07:03,240
Ye Lang loves you deeply.

126
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:05,310
He even turned against Master

127
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:06,560
for your sake.

128
00:07:06,830 --> 00:07:07,920
Why would you do this?

129
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:11,080
I get it now.

130
00:07:11,830 --> 00:07:13,360
You're trying the same trick?

131
00:07:14,270 --> 00:07:15,310
You want Young Master

132
00:07:15,750 --> 00:07:17,600
to end up like your three ex-husbands,

133
00:07:17,630 --> 00:07:18,470
don't you?

134
00:07:19,360 --> 00:07:21,120
Keep a close eye on her.

135
00:07:24,040 --> 00:07:25,480
If anything happens to Ye Lang,

136
00:07:28,750 --> 00:07:30,310
we have countless ways

137
00:07:30,960 --> 00:07:31,830
to make you

138
00:07:31,950 --> 00:07:33,070
wish you were gone.

139
00:07:40,630 --> 00:07:41,470
Ye Lang.

140
00:07:42,270 --> 00:07:43,110
Ye Lang.

141
00:08:00,430 --> 00:08:01,270
Young Master,

142
00:08:02,480 --> 00:08:03,360
I'm sorry.

143
00:08:13,700 --> 00:08:14,540
Dr. Zheng,

144
00:08:14,630 --> 00:08:15,480
the body is here.

145
00:08:23,270 --> 00:08:24,110
You may leave.

146
00:08:34,480 --> 00:08:36,000
I've finally waited

147
00:08:36,720 --> 00:08:38,480
for this perfect body.

148
00:08:48,790 --> 00:08:49,790
Ye Lang,

149
00:08:51,440 --> 00:08:52,320
you fooled me again!

150
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:00,440
Sorry to

151
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:02,160
put you through it.

152
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:04,840
(It's not that bad.)

153
00:09:05,240 --> 00:09:07,120
(I did consider doing this.)

154
00:09:12,390 --> 00:09:13,820
This is nothing.

155
00:09:14,240 --> 00:09:15,110
But,

156
00:09:15,120 --> 00:09:15,960
Young Master,

157
00:09:17,150 --> 00:09:18,510
shouldn't you pay me now?

158
00:09:39,790 --> 00:09:40,720
All good.

159
00:09:43,320 --> 00:09:44,160
So wasn't it him?

160
00:09:58,790 --> 00:09:59,720
Each packet of medicine

161
00:10:00,120 --> 00:10:01,600
only differs by one herb.

162
00:10:04,360 --> 00:10:05,200
I get it now.

163
00:10:13,840 --> 00:10:15,790
These packets each contain a different herb.

164
00:10:17,000 --> 00:10:18,440
Taken in a row, they interact

165
00:10:18,980 --> 00:10:20,220
and create a slow-acting toxin.

166
00:10:21,320 --> 00:10:22,840
It takes two or three months to hit,

167
00:10:23,120 --> 00:10:23,960
hard to notice.

168
00:10:25,780 --> 00:10:27,720
(No wonder I didn't discover it
in my past life.)

169
00:10:28,390 --> 00:10:30,870
(Even Zheng Lu found nothing in this life.)

170
00:10:33,720 --> 00:10:35,000
But that doesn't prove

171
00:10:35,600 --> 00:10:37,360
Butler Zhong is the one behind it.

172
00:10:40,750 --> 00:10:41,960
Then force him to make a move.

173
00:10:44,750 --> 00:10:46,480
(Could it be the one who sent)

174
00:10:46,790 --> 00:10:47,960
(Xiaodi's photo and told me)

175
00:10:48,440 --> 00:10:49,440
(to kill Ye Lang was him?)

176
00:10:50,480 --> 00:10:53,360
(In my past life,
there must have been more to it.)

177
00:11:01,100 --> 00:11:01,990
What are you thinking?

178
00:11:04,720 --> 00:11:05,560
Nothing.

179
00:11:06,440 --> 00:11:07,340
I was just about to ask

180
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:09,240
what you plan to do?

181
00:11:12,720 --> 00:11:13,560
Wanna know?

182
00:11:18,000 --> 00:11:19,390
That costs extra.

183
00:11:22,270 --> 00:11:23,110
Money really

184
00:11:24,270 --> 00:11:25,550
is what drives you.

185
00:11:27,080 --> 00:11:27,920
How much do you want?

186
00:11:32,440 --> 00:11:33,280
500,000?

187
00:11:37,270 --> 00:11:38,110
One more zero.

188
00:11:39,320 --> 00:11:42,790
(Transfer amount)
Let me see...

189
00:11:43,150 --> 00:11:44,030
Five million!

190
00:11:53,440 --> 00:11:55,630
I should've realized Zhong did it.

191
00:11:55,870 --> 00:11:58,000
He is in really poor health.

192
00:11:58,550 --> 00:12:01,320
But Zhong Minghui had no motive.

193
00:12:02,080 --> 00:12:03,030
Killing me

194
00:12:03,480 --> 00:12:05,120
brings him no benefit.

195
00:12:06,600 --> 00:12:07,960
There must be someone behind him.

196
00:12:09,020 --> 00:12:10,220
So someone else wants you dead?

197
00:12:11,030 --> 00:12:11,960
If you die,

198
00:12:11,960 --> 00:12:13,670
make sure your body is mine.

199
00:12:22,080 --> 00:12:22,940
Young Master.

200
00:12:23,000 --> 00:12:24,390
Someone did come to see Mr. Zhong.

201
00:12:34,360 --> 00:12:35,440
How could it be her?

202
00:12:40,510 --> 00:12:41,510
Where's Jiang Xiaodi?

203
00:12:41,750 --> 00:12:42,750
Who's Jiang Xiaodi?

204
00:12:43,240 --> 00:12:44,080
Stop acting.

205
00:12:44,480 --> 00:12:45,600
The day I was leaving,

206
00:12:45,600 --> 00:12:47,030
someone slipped me Xiaodi's photo

207
00:12:47,600 --> 00:12:48,440
and threaten me

208
00:12:48,720 --> 00:12:50,440
to kill Ye Lang, that was you, wasn't it?

209
00:12:50,790 --> 00:12:51,640
Me?

210
00:12:51,670 --> 00:12:52,510
Threaten you?

211
00:12:53,790 --> 00:12:54,630
Ms. Jiang.

212
00:12:55,060 --> 00:12:56,340
You don't know the Li family.

213
00:12:56,940 --> 00:12:57,910
You know even less about

214
00:12:57,910 --> 00:12:58,750
Young Master.

215
00:13:03,440 --> 00:13:04,360
What do you mean?

216
00:13:05,320 --> 00:13:06,360
Using such a trick

217
00:13:06,630 --> 00:13:07,510
to drive us apart

218
00:13:08,240 --> 00:13:09,080
won't work on me.

219
00:13:09,720 --> 00:13:11,480
Ye Lang isn't that simple.

220
00:13:11,870 --> 00:13:13,840
He's best at playing the fool.

221
00:13:14,750 --> 00:13:15,590
Careful.

222
00:13:17,200 --> 00:13:18,750
You might be the one being baited.

223
00:13:20,960 --> 00:13:21,800
Me?

224
00:13:22,910 --> 00:13:24,150
What could Ye Lang want from me?

225
00:13:33,240 --> 00:13:35,240
(So it wasn't Zhong Minghui who sent it?)

226
00:13:36,320 --> 00:13:37,160
(Xiaodi.)

227
00:13:37,480 --> 00:13:38,790
(Where on earth are you?)

228
00:13:47,120 --> 00:13:48,000
Who are you?

229
00:13:48,670 --> 00:13:49,510
Let go of me!

230
00:13:53,790 --> 00:13:54,750
Little brat,

231
00:13:55,270 --> 00:13:56,270
you're pretty sharp.

232
00:13:58,200 --> 00:13:59,390
You will bring us trouble.

233
00:13:59,910 --> 00:14:00,750
Mrs. Liu.

234
00:14:01,440 --> 00:14:02,280
What are you trying to do?

235
00:14:03,550 --> 00:14:05,030
I'm sending you to the pig farm.

236
00:14:23,060 --> 00:14:29,650
♪Stitched-up lips
tear open a blood-red dusk♪

237
00:14:31,460 --> 00:14:37,670
♪You return reborn,
seeing through all my cracks♪

238
00:14:38,220 --> 00:14:45,220
♪This tenderness, a trap or a gift?♪

239
00:14:45,970 --> 00:14:48,440
♪Still, I'd wager my next life on it♪

240
00:14:48,440 --> 00:14:53,440
♪Just for a moment to recognize you again♪

241
00:14:53,440 --> 00:14:57,670
♪You are the blazing light in my despair♪

242
00:14:58,180 --> 00:15:02,110
♪Lighting the edges of my frozen wings♪

243
00:15:02,160 --> 00:15:05,950
♪I burn myself,
leaping into an illusion of fire♪

244
00:15:05,950 --> 00:15:11,700
♪Breaking free
from dead vines in the ashes♪

245
00:15:11,700 --> 00:15:16,020
♪You are the brightest star in the night♪

246
00:15:16,060 --> 00:15:19,880
♪Awakening my dormant fate♪

247
00:15:19,890 --> 00:15:24,380
♪Freeing me from this half-life prison♪

248
00:15:24,410 --> 00:15:29,240
♪As the bells shatter the past♪

249
00:15:29,640 --> 00:15:36,180
♪Life finds its way again♪
